'''Xbox Game Pass'''（簡稱XGP）由[[微軟|微軟]][[Xbox_(品牌)|Xbox]]所提供有關於[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]的[[訂閱|訂閱服務]]。在Xbox Game Pass當中的遊戲庫，適用於[[家用遊戲機|家用遊戲機]]平台的[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]及[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[個人電腦|電腦]]平台的[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]及透過{{le|xCloud|Xbox Cloud Gaming}}[[雲端運算|雲端]]至[[Android|Android]]在[[手機|手機]]上應用遊玩。Xbox Game Pass當中包括部分過往從[[Xbox_(遊戲機)|初代Xbox]]、[[Xbox360|Xbox360]]上推出過的遊戲、至到近年及新推出的遊戲，其中Xbox Game Pass亦包含EA Play的遊戲庫內容<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.xbox.com/zh-HK/games/ea-play |title=透過 EA Play，善加利用遊戲。善加利用您的遊戲更多獎勵、獨家內容，以及無限暢玩更多熱門遊戲。 |access-date=2021-02-14 |archive-date=2022-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220318042315/https://www.xbox.com/zh-HK/games/ea-play }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
[[微軟|微軟]]於2017年2月28日在節目Xbox Insider中初次公開，作為遊戲[[訂閱|訂閱]]的Xbox Game Pass存在。與[[Xbox_Live|Xbox Live Gold]]分開兩者並不會綑綁，即使沒有使用Xbox Live Gold也可獨立使用。<ref name="verge announce">{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/2/28/14761624/xbox-game-pass-subscription-game-service-features-pricing|title=Microsoft's new Xbox Game Pass subscription grants access to more than 100 games|author=Tom Warren|publisher=The Verge|date=February 28, 2017|accessdate=February 28, 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301003629/http://www.theverge.com/2017/2/28/14761624/xbox-game-pass-subscription-game-service-features-pricing|archivedate=March 1, 2017}}</ref>。

在2017年的[[E3遊戲展|E3遊戲展]]中微軟公佈在[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]使用Xbox Game Pass可以遊玩[[Xbox_(遊戲機)|初代Xbox]]開始到[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]的遊戲。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Xbox Oneが初代Xbox下位互換を発表。三世代対応ゲーム機へ - Engadget 日本版|url=http://japanese.engadget.com/jp-2017-06-11-xbox-one-xbox.html|website=Engadget JP|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225095330/https://japanese.engadget.com/jp-2017-06-11-xbox-one-xbox.html}}</ref>並且將會逐漸增添更多畫質提升的遊戲。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/12/e3-2017-xbox-one-original-xbox-backwards-compatibility-details-revealed|title=E3 2017: Xbox One Original Xbox Backwards Compatibility Details Revealed|author=Alex Osborn|website=ign.com|publisher=Ziff Davis, LLC|date=June 11, 2017|accessdate=June 12, 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170612045347/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/12/e3-2017-xbox-one-original-xbox-backwards-compatibility-details-revealed|archivedate=June 12, 2017}}</ref>。

在2018年1月23日微軟發佈Xbox Game Pass消息，表示會一直擴充陣容，第一方的[[Xbox遊戲工作室|Xbox遊戲工作室]]旗下所有新發佈遊戲，將會在發售於平台當日同步登陸Xbox Game Pass陣容當中<ref name="MS-NewGames">{{Cite web|url=https://majornelson.com/2018/01/23/xbox-game-pass-expands-to-include-new-releases-from-microsoft-studios/|title=Xbox Game Pass Expands To Include New Releases From Microsoft Studios|author=Phil Spencer|website=news.xbox.com|publisher=Microsoft Corporation|date=January 23, 2018|accessdate=January 23, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180407014143/https://majornelson.com/2018/01/23/xbox-game-pass-expands-to-include-new-releases-from-microsoft-studios/|archivedate=April 7, 2018}}</ref>。及後在2018年3月20日作為當時的新作《[[盜賊之海|盜賊之海]]》同步登陸在Xbox Game Pass作為新登場作品。其後亦同時發表《{{le|腐朽之都2|State of Decay 2}}》、《[[除暴戰警3|除暴戰警3]]》、《[[極限競速_地平線4|極限競速 地平線4]]》、《[[戰爭機器4|戰爭機器4]]》、[[最後一戰系列|最後一戰系列]]等作品都會登陸，往後相關系列新作亦會與Xbox Game Pass同步<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2018/04/12/robocraft-infinity-available-now-xbox-one-xbox-game-pass/|title=Robocraft Infinity is Available Now Exclusively on Xbox One and Xbox Game Pass|date=April 12, 2018|website=Xbox Wire|accessdate=May 26, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612154659/https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2018/04/12/robocraft-infinity-available-now-xbox-one-xbox-game-pass/|archivedate=June 12, 2018}}</ref>。

[[微軟|微軟]]在2019年5月發表關於Xbox Game Pass的新消息，增加關於[[Windows10|Windows10]]的部分，追加Xbox Game Pass PC、將會提供至少超過一百款PC遊戲<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/30/18644977/microsoft-xbox-games-pass-pc-subscription-service-launch|title=Microsoft is bringing Xbox Game Pass to PC with over 100 titles|first=Nick|author=Statt|date=May 30, 2019|accessdate=May 30, 2019|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530145052/https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/30/18644977/microsoft-xbox-games-pass-pc-subscription-service-launch|archivedate=May 30, 2019}}</ref>。

在2019年4月18日微軟公佈推出將「Xbox Game Pass」與「Xbox Live Gold」兩者合併的「Xbox Game Pass Ultimate」(簡稱XGPU)作為可升級訂閱服務，會於2019年6月9日開始提供有關服務<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/5/18296816/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-subscription-pricing-release-date-rumors|title=Microsoft to combine Xbox Game Pass and Xbox Live into $14.99-a-month subscription|author=Warren|first=Tom|date=April 5, 2019|website=The Verge|accessdate=June 9, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527042744/https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/5/18296816/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-subscription-pricing-release-date-rumors|archivedate=May 27, 2019}}</ref>。同時在2019年6月9日針對Windows10的部分「Game pass for PC」亦會追加包括在XGPU其中<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/6/9/18658682/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-pc-games-xbox-live-pricing-features-e3-2019|title=Microsoft launches Xbox Game Pass Ultimate with PC and Xbox games for $14.99 per month|author=Warren|first=Tom|date=June 9, 2019|website=The Verge|accessdate=June 9, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609204626/https://www.theverge.com/2019/6/9/18658682/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-pc-games-xbox-live-pricing-features-e3-2019|archivedate=June 9, 2019}}</ref>。

微軟在2020年第三季的業績發表、表示使用Xbox Game Pass的會員人數已經超過1000萬人<ref>{{Cite web|author=Kastrenakes|first=Jacob|title=Xbox Game Pass hits 10 million subscribers|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/29/21242004/xbox-game-pass-10-million-subscribers-microsoft-q3-2020-earnings|website=The Verge|publisher=The Verge|accessdate=April 30, 2020|language=en|date=April 29, 2020|archive-date=2020-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200506221230/https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/29/21242004/xbox-game-pass-10-million-subscribers-microsoft-q3-2020-earnings}}</ref>。

2020年9月15日起「Xbox Game Pass Ultimate」再追加新服務，追加[[雲端遊戲|雲端遊戲]]部份的「{{le|Project xCloud}}」，以[[歐美|歐美]]地域為首個服務地區、[[Android|Android]]作為先發平台會有100款以上遊戲作品可以遊玩、[[iOS|iOS]]則當時階段暫未開始作為日後預定追加平台<ref>{{Cite web|title=Microsoft、Project xCloudの日本展開を2021年前半に延期を発表|url=https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/1278866.html|website=GAME Watch|date=2020-09-24|accessdate=2021-01-27|language=ja|last=株式会社インプレス|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522200116/https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/1278866.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/4/21353814/microsoft-xcloud-date-launch-android-xbox-game-pass-ultimate|title=Microsoft’s xCloud game streaming will launch on September 15th on Android|first=Tom|author=Warren|date=August 4, 2020|accessdate=August 4, 2020|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archive-date=2021-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601235608/https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/4/21353814/microsoft-xcloud-date-launch-android-xbox-game-pass-ultimate}}</ref>。

另外在2020年9月初微軟與[[美商藝電|美商藝電]]共同發表、「{{le|EA Play}}」將會在2021年加入於「Xbox Game Pass」陣容、使用PC平台（Windows 10）「Game pass for PC」亦可以遊玩多數的EA發行的作品<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2020/09/09/ea-play-xbox-game-pass-ultimate/|title=EA Play to be included with Xbox Game Pass Ultimate starting this holiday|first=Stephany|author=Nunneley|date=September 9, 2020|accessdate=September 9, 2020|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126050445/https://www.vg247.com/2020/09/09/ea-play-xbox-game-pass-ultimate/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/ea-play-on-xbox-game-pass-for-pc-has-been-delayed-to-2021/|title=EA Play on Xbox Game Pass for PC has been delayed to 2021|first=Tom|author=Ivan|date=December 15, 2020|accessdate=December 15, 2020|website=Video Games Chronicle|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124024227/https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/ea-play-on-xbox-game-pass-for-pc-has-been-delayed-to-2021/}}</ref>。

在2020年9月21日[[微軟|微軟]]公佈使用Xbox Game Pass的會員人數已經超過1500萬人，並且宣佈以75億美元的價格收購[[貝塞斯達軟件|貝塞斯達]]其母公司[[ZeniMax_Media|ZeniMax Media]]以及其旗下全部工作室和IP資產。此次收購後[[毀滅戰士系列|毀滅戰士]]、[[德軍總部系列|德軍總部]]、[[異塵餘生系列|異塵餘生]]、[[上古卷軸系列|上古卷軸]]、[[惡靈附身|邪靈入侵]]等IP遊戲成為Xbox遊戲工作室的第一方IP遊戲<ref>{{Cite web|title=Microsoft to acquire ZeniMax Media and its game publisher Bethesda Softworks|url=https://news.microsoft.com/2020/09/21/microsoft-to-acquire-zenimax-media-and-its-game-publisher-bethesda-softworks/|accessdate=2020-09-21|date=2020-09-21|work=Stories|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202115423/https://news.microsoft.com/2020/09/21/microsoft-to-acquire-zenimax-media-and-its-game-publisher-bethesda-softworks/}}</ref>。

2022年1月17日，[[台灣微軟|台灣微軟]]正式宣布降低台灣地區的Xbox Game Pass價格，PC Game Pass、Xbox Game Pass for Console、[[Xbox_Live_Gold|Xbox Live Gold]]皆從台幣359元調降至199元，而高級會員版本Xbox Game Pass Ultimate則從459調降至299元[https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=226764] {{Wayback|url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=226764 |date=20220418011907 }}

== 訂閱服務與內容 ==
* 「Xbox Game Pass for Console」。對象平台：[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]。
* 「PC Game Pass」（原名Xbox Game Pass for PC）<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theverge.com/2021/12/9/22827140/microsoft-pc-game-pass-naming-rebrand | title = Microsoft rebrands Xbox Game Pass for PC to just PC Game Pass | first = Tom | last = Warren | date = 2021-12-09 | accessdate = 2021-12-09 | work = [[The_Verge|The Verge]] | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172241/https://www.theverge.com/2021/12/9/22827140/microsoft-pc-game-pass-naming-rebrand }}</ref>。對象平台：[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]、[[Windows_11|Windows 11]]。
* 「Project xCloud」。對象平台：{{le|xCloud|Xbox Cloud Gaming}} ([[Android|Android]] / [[Windows|Windows]])。
*「Xbox Game Pass Ultimate」。對象平台：[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]、[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]、[[Windows_11|Windows 11]]、{{le|xCloud|Xbox Cloud Gaming}} ([[Android|Android]] / [[Windows|Windows]])。

